Plot

Hitoshi Nagano (Kazuya Kamenashi), who works at an electronics store, picks 
up a cellphone left behind by a customer and goes about a scam. He calls 
the person's mother and pretends to be her son. He then gets the mother to 
transfer money to his bank account. Soon, Hitoshi gets a lot more than he 
bargained for.
